'''Bluestone Lake''', located in the [[City/Legends|city]] [[Ussa]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Bellassa/Legends|Bellassa]], was the one of the seven [[lake]]s within the city boundaries, and gave its name to the surrounding city district. [[Bluestone District]] was adjacent to [[Cloud Lake]] District and the Commons. It was home to a large market.

==Appearances==
